{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883622189,"sessionID":"ses_285178ea0ffepODHz0C64Ihxdr","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae99346001A2jBTvzCctbnGE","messageID":"msg_d7ae97ba1001AyD5vypoc3VADg","sessionID":"ses_285178ea0ffepODHz0C64Ihxdr","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_81809fe43eee4b1996b9abc1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-040/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-040/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for testing the Python SDK and CLI functionality.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-040\n10: - **Module**: `sdk-python/tests`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Scenario: TODO\n17: \n18: ### AR-040-001: TBD\n19: \n20: - **GIVEN** \n21: - **WHEN** \n22: - **THEN** \n23: \n24: ---\n\n(End of file - total 24 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for testing the Python SDK and CLI functionality.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-040\n- **Module**: `sdk-python/tests`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: TODO\n\n### AR-040-001: TBD\n\n- **GIVEN** ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-040/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775883622180,"end":1775883622187}}}}
